CustomSlowmode 

Easily modify the slowmode values that you can set on channels!
No more are the days of 5-second slowmode; use 1 second instead so your members aren't waiting in agony.

Download: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spinfal/enmity-plugins/master/dist/CustomSlowmode.js
Source: https://github.com/spinfal/enmity-plugins/tree/master/CustomSlowmode
